  "detailed_description": "The world keeps changing. Unfortunately, not all things work out for the best. Some animals are endangered. As a driver, you will help transport these innocent creatures to be rescued from poaching. You will meet all kinds of species: rhinos, zebras, oxen that need a new home. Be careful how you drive, they are sensitive to it because they are wild. In this way you will also contribute to saving the lives of these wonderful creatures!<br><br><strong>Game features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 9 levels<br></li><li>Sharp Turns<br></li><li>Big trailer that holds these animals ( rhynos,zebras,oxen)<br></li><li></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "The world keeps changing. Unfortunately, not all things work out for the best. Some animals are endangered. As a driver, you will help transport these innocent creatures to be rescued from poaching. You will meet all kinds of species: rhinos, zebras, oxen that need a new home. Be careful how you drive, they are sensitive to it because they are wild. In this way you will also contribute to saving the lives of these wonderful creatures!<br><br><strong>Game features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 9 levels<br></li><li>Sharp Turns<br></li><li>Big trailer that holds these animals ( rhynos,zebras,oxen)<br></li><li></li></ul>",
